qMetaDef.title: Token Consumption by Month
qMetaDef.description:
Measure the approximate tokens used per month by login access rules and user access passes.
This data is not valid at a level below Month due to the 28-day regenerative nature of login access passes.

qMetaDef.title: Token Consumption over Last 28 Days with AppId
qMetaDef.description: Use this chart in case you have multiple apps with the same name in the same Stream. It includes AppId to distinguish the apps.

qExpression.qv:
ceil(count({<[Access Type]={'Login Access'},LogTimeStamp= {">=$(=daystart(max(LogTimeStamp)-27)"}>} distinct UsageId)/10)
+count({<[Access Type]={'User Access'},LogTimeStamp= {">=$(=daystart(max(LogTimeStamp)-27))"}>} distinct UserId)

ceil(count({<[Access Type]={'Login Access'},LogTimeStamp= {">=$(=daystart(max(LogTimeStamp)-27)"}>} distinct UsageId)/10) +count({<[Access Type]={'User Access'},LogTimeStamp= {">=$(=daystart(max(LogTimeStamp)-27))"}>} distinct UserId)

qDef.qDef: [Tokens for Login Access]+[Tokens for User Access]

(ceil(count({<[Access Type]={'Login Access'},LogTimeStamp= {">=$(=daystart(max(LogTimeStamp)-28))"}>} distinct UsageId)/10)
+
count({<[Access Type]={'User Access'},LogTimeStamp= {">=$(=daystart(max(LogTimeStamp)-28))"}>} distinct UserId)
)
/
(
ceil(count({<[Access Type]={'Login Access'},LogTimeStamp= {">=$(=daystart(max(LogTimeStamp)-28))"}>} distinct TOTAL UsageId)/10)
+ 
count({<[Access Type]={'User Access'},LogTimeStamp= {">=$(=daystart(max(LogTimeStamp)-28))"}>} distinct TOTAL UserId)
)

qCalcCond.qv: count({<[Access Type]={'Login Access'},LogTimeStamp= {">=$(=daystart(max(LogTimeStamp)-28))"}>} distinct UsageId) +count({<[Access Type]={'User Access'},LogTimeStamp= {">=$(=daystart(max(LogTimeStamp)-28))"}>} distinct UserId)>0
